---
// Interactive 3-Step Methodology Component
---

<section class="py-24 bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark relative overflow-hidden" id="methodology">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 z-10 relative">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span class="text-primary font-bold text-sm mb-2 block tracking-widest uppercase" data-i18n="methodology.eyebrow">Cómo trabajamos</span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6" data-i18n="methodology.title">
        Nuestra metodología
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto" data-i18n="methodology.intro">
        Un proceso probado de tres pasos para transformar ideas abstractas en productos digitales robustos, comenzando desde la estrategia hasta la ejecución ágil.
      </p>
    </div>

    {/* Expanding Cards Container */}
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row w-full h-[800px] md:h-[500px] gap-4 md:gap-6 group/container">
      
      {/* Step 1: Business Understanding */}
      <div class="methodology-card relative flex-[1] hover:flex-[3] md:hover:flex-[4] transition-all duration-700 ease-[cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1)] cursor-pointer overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-100 to-slate-200 dark:from-slate-800 dark:to-slate-900 border border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-700 shadow-lg group/card flex flex-col justify-end md:justify-start">
        {/* Background Graphic */}
        <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20 transition-opacity duration-700 group-hover/card:opacity-100 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_bottom_right,var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-primary/40 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
        
        {/* Number Badge */}
        <div class="absolute top-6 left-6 z-20">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 shadow-md flex items-center justify-center text-primary font-black text-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700">
            01
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Content Container */}
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col justify-end p-8 z-20 transition-transform duration-700 md:translate-y-8 group-hover/card:translate-y-0">
          <h3 class="hidden md:flex absolute inset-0 items-center justify-center text-3xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 dark:text-white text-center opacity-90 -translate-y-8 transition-opacity duration-500 group-hover/card:opacity-0 pointer-events-none" data-i18n="methodology.step1.title">
            Entendimiento del negocio
          </h3>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-primary bg-white/80 dark:bg-slate-800/80 p-3 rounded-2xl backdrop-blur-sm shadow-sm md:-translate-x-4 transition-all duration-700 group-hover/card:translate-x-0">
              handshake
            </span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white whitespace-nowrap transition-all duration-700 group-hover/card:text-primary opacity-0 -translate-x-8 group-hover/card:opacity-100 group-hover/card:translate-x-0 hidden md:block" data-i18n="methodology.step1.title">
              Entendimiento del negocio
            </h3>
            {/* Mobile Horizontal Title (always visible on mobile) */}
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white whitespace-nowrap md:hidden" data-i18n="methodology.step1.title">
              Entendimiento del negocio
            </h3>
          </div>
          
          {/* Expanding Tooltip / Description */}
          <div class="grid grid-rows-[0fr] group-hover/card:grid-rows-[1fr] transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-700 md:opacity-0 md:group-hover/card:opacity-100 ease-[cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1)]">
            <div class="overflow-hidden">
              <div class="pt-2">
                <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 text-lg leading-relaxed relative" data-i18n="methodology.step1.desc">
                  La etapa consultiva. Entendemos a fondo tu panorama estratégico, ecosistema de marketing y competencia. Analizamos tus objetivos de negocio, descubrimos cómo funciona tu cultura organizacional e identificamos tus necesidades y desafíos tecnológicos.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-6 flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white/50 dark:bg-slate-900/50 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700" data-i18n="methodology.step1.tags.0">Estrategia</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white/50 dark:bg-slate-900/50 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700" data-i18n="methodology.step1.tags.1">Consultoría</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white/50 dark:bg-slate-900/50 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700" data-i18n="methodology.step1.tags.2">Metas</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      {/* Step 2: Discovery */}
      <div class="methodology-card relative flex-[1] md:flex-[2] hover:flex-[3] md:hover:flex-[4] transition-all duration-700 ease-[cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1)] cursor-pointer overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-100 to-slate-200 dark:from-slate-800 dark:to-slate-900 border border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-700 shadow-lg group/card flex flex-col justify-end md:justify-start">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20 transition-opacity duration-700 group-hover/card:opacity-100 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_bottom_right,var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-accent/40 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
        
        <div class="absolute top-6 left-6 z-20">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 shadow-md flex items-center justify-center text-accent font-black text-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700">
            02
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col justify-end p-8 z-20 transition-transform duration-700 md:translate-y-8 group-hover/card:translate-y-0">
          <h3 class="hidden md:flex absolute inset-0 items-center justify-center text-3xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 dark:text-white text-center opacity-90 -translate-y-8 transition-opacity duration-500 group-hover/card:opacity-0 pointer-events-none" data-i18n="methodology.step2.title">
            Descubrimiento
          </h3>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-accent bg-white/80 dark:bg-slate-800/80 p-3 rounded-2xl backdrop-blur-sm shadow-sm md:-translate-x-4 transition-all duration-700 group-hover/card:translate-x-0">
              travel_explore
            </span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white whitespace-nowrap transition-all duration-700 group-hover/card:text-accent opacity-0 -translate-x-8 group-hover/card:opacity-100 group-hover/card:translate-x-0 hidden md:block" data-i18n="methodology.step2.title">
              Descubrimiento
            </h3>
            {/* Mobile Horizontal Title */}
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white whitespace-nowrap md:hidden" data-i18n="methodology.step2.title">
              Descubrimiento
            </h3>
          </div>
          
          <div class="grid grid-rows-[1fr] md:grid-rows-[0fr] group-hover/card:grid-rows-[1fr] transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-700 md:opacity-0 md:group-hover/card:opacity-100 ease-[cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1)]">
            <div class="overflow-hidden">
              <div class="pt-2">
                <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 text-lg leading-relaxed relative" data-i18n="methodology.step2.desc">
                  Comenzamos a iterar. Utilizamos metodologías centradas en el usuario como Design Thinking para explorar posibilidades y probar hipótesis. Solo cuando la visión del producto alcanza una claridad absoluta, avanzamos al siguiente paso.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-6 flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white/50 dark:bg-slate-900/50 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700" data-i18n="methodology.step2.tags.0">Design Thinking</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white/50 dark:bg-slate-900/50 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700" data-i18n="methodology.step2.tags.1">Iteración UX</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white/50 dark:bg-slate-900/50 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700" data-i18n="methodology.step2.tags.2">Prototipado</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      {/* Step 3: Agile Building */}
      <div class="methodology-card relative flex-[1] hover:flex-[3] md:hover:flex-[4] transition-all duration-700 ease-[cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1)] cursor-pointer overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-100 to-slate-200 dark:from-slate-800 dark:to-slate-900 border border-slate-300 dark:border-slate-700 shadow-lg group/card flex flex-col justify-end md:justify-start">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20 transition-opacity duration-700 group-hover/card:opacity-100 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_bottom_right,var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-green-500/40 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
        
        <div class="absolute top-6 left-6 z-20">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 shadow-md flex items-center justify-center text-green-500 font-black text-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700">
            03
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col justify-end p-8 z-20 transition-transform duration-700 md:translate-y-8 group-hover/card:translate-y-0">
          <h3 class="hidden md:flex absolute inset-0 items-center justify-center text-3xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 dark:text-white text-center opacity-90 -translate-y-8 transition-opacity duration-500 group-hover/card:opacity-0 pointer-events-none" data-i18n="methodology.step3.title">
            Construcción ágil
          </h3>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-green-500 bg-white/80 dark:bg-slate-800/80 p-3 rounded-2xl backdrop-blur-sm shadow-sm md:-translate-x-4 transition-all duration-700 group-hover/card:translate-x-0">
              rocket_launch
            </span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white whitespace-nowrap transition-all duration-700 group-hover/card:text-green-500 opacity-0 -translate-x-8 group-hover/card:opacity-100 group-hover/card:translate-x-0 hidden md:block" data-i18n="methodology.step3.title">
              Construcción ágil
            </h3>
            {/* Mobile Horizontal Title */}
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white whitespace-nowrap md:hidden" data-i18n="methodology.step3.title">
              Construcción ágil
            </h3>
          </div>
          
          <div class="grid grid-rows-[0fr] group-hover/card:grid-rows-[1fr] transition-[grid-template-rows] duration-700 md:opacity-0 md:group-hover/card:opacity-100 ease-[cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1)]">
            <div class="overflow-hidden">
              <div class="pt-2">
                <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 text-lg leading-relaxed relative" data-i18n="methodology.step3.desc">
                  Con requerimientos claros, activamos metodologías ágiles (Scrum/Kanban) para comenzar a construir. Desarrollamos tu proyecto en sprints técnicos que garantizan velocidad de entrega y transparencia total.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-6 flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white/50 dark:bg-slate-900/50 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700" data-i18n="methodology.step3.tags.0">Scrum</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white/50 dark:bg-slate-900/50 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700" data-i18n="methodology.step3.tags.1">Desarrollo Frontend/Backend</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white/50 dark:bg-slate-900/50 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700" data-i18n="methodology.step3.tags.2">CI/CD</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>